#ad Manhattans are the new espresso martinis.✨Especially when they’re made with Crown Royal Fine De Luxe, the ultimate Canadian whisky. 

Here's the recipe so you can serve them at your holiday parties: 

WHAT YOU NEED 
1.25 oz. Crown Royal Fine De Luxe Blended Canadian Whisky 
0.25 oz. sweet vermouth 
1 dash bitters 
1 rosemary, cherry or garnish of your choice 

HOW TO MAKE IT 
Stir ingredients together in an ice-filled mixing glass. 
Pour into a glass. 
Garnish! 

#CrownRoyalCanada #HostingwithCrown #enjoyresponsibly
